Package: cardelino
Type: Package
Title: Clone Identification from Single Cell Data
Version: 0.6.1
Date: 2019-08-10
Authors@R: c(person("Davis", "McCarthy", role=c("aut", "cre"),
        email="davis@ebi.ac.uk"), person("Yuanhua", "Huang", 
        role=c("aut"), email="yuanhua@ebi.ac.uk"))
Maintainer: Davis McCarthy <davis@ebi.ac.uk>
Description: Methods to infer clonal structure for a population of cells using 
    single-cell RNA-seq data (and possibly other data modalities). Methods to 
    assign cells to inferred clones and explore differences in gene expression
    between clones.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 3.4), stats
Imports: ggplot2, ggpubr, ggtree, pheatmap, matrixStats, Matrix, doMC, foreach,
    vcfR, GenomeInfoDb, GenomicRanges, methods, snpStats, S4Vectors, 
    VariantAnnotation
Suggests: BiocStyle, knitr, pcaMethods, testthat, combinat, VGAM
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyData: true
biocViews: SingleCell, RNASeq, Visualization, Transcriptomics, GeneExpression, 
    Sequencing, Software
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
NeedsCompilation: yes
URL: https://github.com/PMBio/cardelino
BugReports: https://github.com/PMBio/cardelino/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
